+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
|   long options    |   short    |    vaue type     |description |
|                   |  options   |                  |            |
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
|      --help       |     h      |     boolean      | show this  |
|                   |            |                  |    help    |
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
|     --version     |     v      |     boolean      |show version|
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
|   --decompress    |     d      |     boolean      | decompress |
|                   |            |                  | input data |
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
|                   |            |     [-1..9]|     |compression |
|--compression-level|     l      |none|default|speed|   level    |
|                   |            |                  |            |
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
|                   |            |                  |input buffer|
| --in-buffer-size  |    ibs     |      size_t      |    size    |
|                   |            |                  |            |
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
| --out-buffer-size |    obs     |      size_t      |   output   |
|                   |            |                  |buffer size |
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
|     --in-file     |     i      |      string      | read data  |
|                   |            |                  |from a file |
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
|    --out-file     |     o      |      string      | write data |
|                   |            |                  | to a file  |
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
|                   |            |                  |  to load   |
|     --in-conf     |     c      |      string      |  settings  |
|                   |            |                  |from a file |
+-------------------+------------+------------------+------------+
size_t:[1..%zu]
